1. Customer Application → Applicant submits personal/business details, loan amount, purpose
2. Document Upload → Income proof, ID, bank statements, collateral documents
3. Credit Check → Automated scoring, external credit bureau integration
4. Risk Assessment → Manual review by loan officers, verification calls
5. Approval Workflow → Multi-level approval based on loan amount
6. Disbursement → Funds transfer upon approval
7. Repayment Tracking → EMI schedules, payment processing
8. Collections → Late payment handling, reminders

// Database/migrations/
1. users (with role: officer, loan officer, moderator, admin)
2. loans (status: draft, submitted, under_review, approved, rejected, cancelled, disbursed, closed)
3. loan_applications
4. documents
5. credit_scores
6. repayments
7. transactions
8. approvals (workflow)
9. notifications
10. audit_logs


=====================================================

// API Routes

1. Authentication & User Management
POST   /api/borrower/register      // Applicant registration
POST   /api/borrower/login         // Applicant login
POST   /api/borrower/logout        // Applicant logout
GET    /api/borrower/profile       // View Applicant profile
PUT    /api/borrower/profile       // Update Applicant profile

GET    /api/user/login             // System user login
POST   /api/user/logout            // System user logout
GET    /api/user/profile           // Get System user profile
PUT    /api/user/profile           // Update System user profile

2. Loan Application Flow
GET    /api/borrower/applications                  // Get all loan applications for Applicant
POST   /api/borrower/applications                  // Create a new loan application
GET    /api/borrower/applications/{uuid}           // Get specific application
PUT    /api/borrower/applications/{uuid}/cancel    // Cancel application
POST   /api/borrower/applications/{uuid}/documents // Upload supporting docs
POST   /api/borrower/applications/{uuid}/submit    // Submit the created application

3. Document Management
POST   /api/borrower/applications/{uuid}/upload                // upload document
GET    /api/borrower/applications/{application_id}/documents   // View document (with permission)
DELETE /api/borrower/applications/{uuid}/delete                // Remove document
POST   /api/documents/{document_id}/verify                     // Officer marks doc as verified

4. Loan Assessment API
POST   /api/credit-check           // Internal scoring algorithm
GET    /api/credit-score/{user_id} // Get credit score
POST   /api/external-credit        // Mock external bureau integration

5. Approval Workflow
GET    /api/applications                // List pending applications
POST   /api/applications/{uuid}/assign  // Assign to officer
POST   /api/admin/approve               // Under review/Approve/Reject the application (with hierarchy check)
GET    /api/admin/approval-history      // Audit trail

6. Disbursement & Payment
POST   /api/disbursement/{loan_id}          // Release funds
GET    /api/repayment-schedule/{loan_id}    // EMI schedule
POST   /api/repayment/pay                   // Record payment
GET    /api/repayment/history/{loan_id}     // Payment history
POST   /api/repayment/reminder              // Send payment reminder

7. Reporting & Analytics
GET    /api/reports/loans-overview      // Dashboard stats
GET    /api/reports/npa                 // Non-performing assets
GET    /api/reports/approved-loans      // Approved loans report
GET    /api/reports/export-excel        // Export to Excel
GET    /api/reports/generate-pdf        // Generate PDF statement

